THE man accused of killing Karabo Mokoena was denied bail in the Johannesburg Magistrate's Court today.Mantsoe said in his affidavit that he started dating Karabo in October 2016.He also denied that he had cuts on his body and that him and Karabo had shared blood.Mantsoe said Karabo was suicidal at the time of her death.He claims to have found Karabo dead when he returned to the flat.He then decided to dispose of her body as he had panicked because he knew Karabo had claimed he was abusing her. However the state says there was no evidence that Karabo was suicidal.